name: Gel Kayano 22 GS
description:
The new GEL-Kayano? 22 GS shoe introduces full-length
FluidRide? midsole technology for the first time in ASICS youth
specific running collection. Dynamic DuoMax? Support System
and GEL? Cushioning System create a premium ride while the fun
new upper is both comfortable and secure. Built specifically for
developing athletes, with a 3mm Heel Raise and softer Youth-
Specific Cushioning.
